# CueYori Cursor Rules

- Use Expo Router for navigation.
- Use TypeScript everywhere.
- Use Zustand for local state.
- Use Expo Notifications for local cooking cues.
- Keep business logic out of screens; put cooking logic under `src/features/cooking`.
- Keep notification scheduling under `src/services/notifications`.
- Prefer small components.
- No backend until MVP workflow works locally.
- UI should feel premium, calm, and native.
- Every cooking action should map to a clear next user action.
